#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.nanprod.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.nanprod"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanprod.nanprod:1 of
msgid ""
"Return the product of array elements over a given axis treating Not a "
"Numbers (NaNs) as ones."
msgstr "返回给定轴上数组元素的乘积，将非数字（NaN）视为1。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanprod.nanprod:4 of
msgid "One is returned for slices that are all-NaN or empty."
msgstr "对于全为NaN或空的切片，返回1。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanprod.nanprod of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanprod.nanprod:6 of
msgid ""
"Tensor containing numbers whose product is desired. If `a` is not an "
"tensor, a conversion is attempted."
msgstr "包含所需乘积的张量。如果`a`不是一个张量，则尝试进行转换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanprod.nanprod:9 of
msgid ""
"Axis along which the product is computed. The default is to compute the "
"product of the flattened tensor."
msgstr "计算乘积的轴。默认计算展平张量的乘积。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanprod.nanprod:12 of
msgid ""
"The type of the returned tensor and of the accumulator in which the "
"elements are summed.  By default, the dtype of `a` is used.  An exception"
" is when `a` has an integer type with less precision than the platform "
"(u)intp. In that case, the default will be either (u)int32 or (u)int64 "
"depending on whether the platform is 32 or 64 bits. For inexact inputs, "
"dtype must be inexact."
msgstr ""
"返回张量的类型和元素相加的累加器类型。默认情况下，使用`a`的dtype。一个"
"例外情况是当`a`具有比平台(u)intp精度低的整数类型时。在这种情况下，默认值"
"将是(u)int32或(u)int64，具体取决于平台是32位还是64位。对于不精确的输入，"
"dtype必须是不精确的。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanprod.nanprod:19 of
msgid ""
"Alternate output tensor in which to place the result.  The default is "
"``None``. If provided, it must have the same shape as the expected "
"output, but the type will be cast if necessary.  See `doc.ufuncs` for "
"details. The casting of NaN to integer can yield unexpected results."
msgstr ""
"用于放置结果的替代输出张量。默认为``None``。如果提供，它必须具有与预期"
"输出相同的形状，但如有必要，类型将被转换。详情请参见`doc.ufuncs`。将NaN"
"转换为整数可能会产生意外结果。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanprod.nanprod:25 of
msgid ""
"If True, the axes which are reduced are left in the result as dimensions "
"with size one. With this option, the result will broadcast correctly "
"against the original `arr`."
msgstr ""
"如果为True，则在结果中保留被归约的轴作为大小为1的维度。使用此选项，结果将"
"能够正确地与原始`arr`进行广播。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanprod.nanprod of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanprod.nanprod:30 of
msgid ""
"**nanprod** -- A new tensor holding the result is returned unless `out` "
"is specified, in which case it is returned."
msgstr ""
"**nanprod** -- 返回一个保存结果的新张量，除非指定了`out`，在这种情况下"
"返回它。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanprod.nanprod of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanprod.nanprod:36 of
msgid ":py:obj:`mt.prod`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanprod.nanprod:37 of
msgid "Product across array propagating NaNs."
msgstr "跨数组传播NaN的乘积。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanprod.nanprod:39 of
msgid ":py:obj:`isnan`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanprod.nanprod:40 of
msgid "Show which elements are NaN."
msgstr "显示哪些元素是NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanprod.nanprod:43 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

